descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 2 Spells that are pretty much overpowered but very Funny!

The First spell called Jesse\'s Spell which has 7 different effects: Candle Light, Marked for Death, Unrenteling Force, Fire Breath, Fire bolt, Disarm and last but not least Paralys

The Second Spell is called OVERPOWERED SPELL it has 2 diferent effects and is just for fun cuz it doesn\'t kill anyone, it makes them just fly around totally paralyzed, so i think you can already guess which spells they are! ;) 

hope you have fun with these 2 SpellTomes and Endorse ?

LOCATION: on the second floor in the riverwood trader on his nightdesk i will add some pictures

I\'ve added a video of some gameplay from this mod hope you like it!
